95 misdemeanor.
96 (d) Nothing in this Code section shall be construed to permit the prosecution of:
97 (1) Any person for conduct relating to an abortion for which the consent of the pregnant
98 woman, or person authorized by law to act on her behalf, has been obtained or for which
99 such consent is implied by law;
100 (2) Any person for any medical treatment of the pregnant woman or her unborn child;
101 or
